item.description:
• This Anti-Theft Backpack apply anti-theft design technology. Zipper of main pocket is fully hidden in the back of this bag ,no theft will easily open your backpack.Water Repellent Material - This backpack is made of Water Repellent Material so now you can travel carefree without worrying about water splashes or rain.
  • Superior & Durability: Made of durable and Eco-friendly water resistant oxford textile fabric,which keeps your files and stuffs dry inside. This backpack can hold up to 15.6" laptop from most brands; USB Charge External USB port with built-in charging cable offers a convenient charging of your electronic device anywhere, and this bag do not include a battery, you need a power bank to charge it.
  • Anti Theft Pocket - This bag comes with an anti theft secret pocket on the backside to keep money / passport and other small valuables safe while travelling as these pockets are not accessible when you are wearing the backpack.
  • The backpack features a sleek and ergonomic design with a balanced weight distribution through its straps. This makes this product a suitable alternative to bulky and unsightly backpacks. The compact design of this backpack helps you to rest it comfortably on your shoulders while accommodating all your essentials with ease.
